"title": "4402: plants",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4402",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Plants are an important aspect of God's creation, and a major source of food and materials. Scripture refers to many plants, with their various uses.</p>\n<h2>Plants as a source of food</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:29-Gen1:30\">GEN 1:29–1:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:11-Gen1:12\">GEN 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:3\">GEN 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:14\">PSA 104:14</a></p>\n<h2>Growth of plants dependent upon soil, sun and irrigation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:2\">DEU 32:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:4-Gen2:5\">GEN 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:26\">2KI 19:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:27\">ISA 37:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:16-Job8:19\">JOB 8:16–8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:11\">ISA 61:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:1\">ZEC 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:3-Matt13:8\">MAT 13:3–13:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:3-Mark4:8\">MRK 4:3–4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:5-Luke8:8\">LUK 8:5–8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:11\">JAS 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Individual plants</h2>\n<h3>Aloes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:5-Num24:6\">NUM 24:5–24:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:8\">PSA 45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:17\">PRO 7:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:13-Song4:14\">SNG 4:13–4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Calamus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:20\">JER 6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:12-Song4:14\">SNG 4:12–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:24\">ISA 43:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:19\">EZK 27:19</a></p>\n<h3>Crocus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1-Isa35:2\">ISA 35:1–35:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Hyssop</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:33\">1KI 4:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22\">EXO 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:7\">PSA 51:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a></p>\n<h3>Lily</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:27\">LUK 12:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28-Matt6:29\">MAT 6:28–6:29</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:1-Song2:2\">SNG 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:5\">HOS 14:5</a></p>\n<h3>Lotus</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:21-Job40:22\">JOB 40:21–40:22</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Mandrake</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:13\">SNG 7:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:14-Gen30:16\">GEN 30:14–30:16</a></p>\n<h3>Mustard</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:31-Matt13:32\">MAT 13:31–13:32</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:30-Mark4:32\">MRK 4:30–4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:18-Luke13:19\">LUK 13:18–13:19</a></p>\n<h3>Myrtle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:13\">ISA 55:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:18-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:18–41:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:8-Zech1:10\">ZEC 1:8–1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Reed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:3\">EXO 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:11\">JOB 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:6-Isa19:7\">ISA 19:6–19:7</a></p>\n<h3>Rose</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:1\">SNG 2:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Rush</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:6-Isa19:7\">ISA 19:6–19:7</a></strong></p>",
